%8F%AB%E8%BD%A6%E9%AA%97%E5%B1%80/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 00:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E4%B8%87%E9%A1%BA%E5%8F%AB%E8%BD%A6%E9%AA%97%E5%B1%80/</guid><description>交几千块加盟费就能跑网约车、月入过万？万顺叫车让无数司机血本无归。这种加盟模式的法律问题在哪？</description></item><item><title>花三万块请人代运营拼多多店铺，一个月卖了三单——钱能要回来吗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E6%8B%BC%E5%A4%9A%E5%A4%9A%E4%BB%A3%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E9%AA%97%E5%B1%80/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E6%8B%BC%E5%A4%9A%E5%A4%9A%E4%BB%A3%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E9%AA%97%E5%B1%80/</guid><description>代运营公司承诺月销过万，收了钱之后店铺根本没流量。这是服务纠纷还是诈骗？怎么把钱要回来？</description></item></channel></rss>